{\phi}}
{\nonumber}
\\
&&
-e^{-\sqrt{\frac{2}{3}}\chi}\dot{{\phi}}^{2}\mathcal{K}_{B 
{\phi}}+\frac{1}{2}e^{-\sqrt{\frac{2}{3}}\chi}\dot{{\phi}}^{2}\mathcal{G}_{{\phi}{\phi}}
